I '''Elmore John Leonard, Jr.''' (Octubre 11, 1925&nbsp;– Agosto 20, 2013) metung yang Americanung nobelista ampong talasulat senaryo  (''screenwriter''). [[Western fiction|Western]] la reng minuna nang milimbag a nobela, oneng kalabas ning panaun megi nong espesyalisasyun Leonard deng [[crime fiction]] ampong [[suspense thriller]], at dakal kareti, megawang pelikula.

Kayabe la kareng pikabaluan nang diling obra deng ''[[Get Shorty]]'', ''[[Out of Sight]]'', ''[[Hombre (novel)|Hombre]]'', ''[[Mr. Majestyk]]'', ampong ''[[Rum Punch]]'' (a mibage king pelikula king ''[[Jackie Brown (pelikula)|Jackie Brown]]''). Kayabe la kareng makuyad a salita nang Leonard deng megawang pelikulang ''[[Three-Ten to Yuma|3:10 to Yuma]]'' ampong ''[[The Tall T]]'', ampo ing kasalungsungan dang [[FX (network)|FX]] a seryeng telebisyon ''[[Justified (TV series)|Justified]]''.

